      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to the man’s son, who was interviewed by the news crew, his father “loved to tinker with things.” Apparently, he considered working on cars and figuring out how to fix different problems on them a challenge. That’s understandable, but as the son point out, “what’s he going to do now?”",
